  "prompt": "What are some recipes using 4 ounces of steak?",
  "response": "Here are some recipes that use 4 ounces of steak:\n\n1. Steak Salad\n- Slice steak and serve over mixed greens\n- Add cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and your favorite dressing\n\n2. Steak Fajitas\n- Slice steak into thin strips\n- Saut\u00e9 with bell peppers and onions\n- Serve with tortillas and toppings\n\n3. Steak Stir-Fry\n- Cut steak into bite-sized pieces\n- Stir-fry with vegetables like broccoli, carrots, and snap peas\n- Serve over rice\n\n4. Steak Sandwich\n- Slice steak thinly\n- Place on toasted bread with arugula and mustard\n- Add cheese if desired\n\n5. Steak Tacos\n- Season and grill steak\n- Chop into small pieces\n- Serve in corn tortillas with salsa and cilantro\n\n6. Steak and Eggs\n- Pan-sear steak\n- Serve with scrambled or fried eggs\n- Great for breakfast or brunch\n\n7. Steak Kebabs\n- Cut steak into cubes\n- Skewer with vegetables\n- Grill or broil\n\nThese recipes provide variety while using a 4-ounce portion of steak.",
